---
title: HelloHero: Pork Schnitzel & Herby Mash with Garlicky Veggies & Garlic Hollandaise
description: Here's a neat trick: when you're crumbing food, use one hand for the wet ingredients and the other for the dry so you don't end up with fingers that look like hotdogs! Give it a try when you make these golden pork schnitzels.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6780745219b5d36400fb18b2-b45bf1b0.jpeg
